cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CR, cs.MA 

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on Cellular Vehicle-to-Everything (C-V2X) communication and the performance analysis of this technology. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses autonomous vehicles and their mobility. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper deals with the performance analysis of a communication system. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as the paper may touch upon security concerns related to C-V2X communication. 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is also less likely but possible as the paper may discuss the coordination and communication between multiple agents (i.e. vehicles) in a system.
